headlines.title: Paramount to cut 3% of U.S. workforce as it deepens cost-cutting
headlines.description: It's the latest round of layoffs at Paramount as it contends with cord-cutting and prepares to merge with Skydance Media.

headlines.title: Conservative Sen. Josh Hawley wants to raise federal minimum wage
headlines.description: GOP Sen. Josh Hawley's position on the minimum wage aligns him with some of the Senate's most liberal members.

headlines.title: Despite three-owner structure, NFL rules require Carlie Irsay-Gordon to have unilateral control
headlines.description: On Monday, the Colts announced an "ownership transition" that has the three daughters of the late Jim Irsay serving as owners of the franchise.

headlines.title: Several people killed in school shooting in Austria's second biggest city, police say
headlines.description: At least eight people were killed and several others injured in a school shooting Tuesday in the southern Austrian city of Graz, local media reported

headlines.title: Stock market today: Live updates
headlines.description: The S&P 500 inched higher to post its second straight positive session on Monday.

headlines.title: US and China Talk Trade as Fight Over Rare Earths Escalates
headlines.description: Officials from the world’s largest economies will try to strike a deal Tuesday to relax painful export restrictions that they have imposed on each other.

headlines.title: Wall Street CEOs go through the five stages of tariff grief : NPR
headlines.description: As they process President Trump's chaotic tariffs and other economic policies, some of the country's most powerful CEOs are moving from denial and bargaining to public anger and depression.

headlines.title: Meta Is Creating a New A.I. Lab to Pursue ‘Superintelligence’
headlines.description: The new lab, set to include Scale AI founder Alexandr Wang, is part of a reorganization of Meta’s artificial intelligence efforts under Mark Zuckerberg.

headlines.title: Uber taps AI firm Wayve to pilot fully driverless rides in the UK
headlines.description: The ride-hailing app said the pilot would be the first of its kind for the company, as it allow users to take Uber rides without a safety driver present.

headlines.title: Android 16 will officially launch later today
headlines.description: In wake of Apple's unveiling of iOS 26, Google has officially confirmed that we'll see the "final" Android 16 launch later today.
